<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.baseHeadContent %>

    <title><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %></title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="A tracking system for your Animal Crossing New Horizons fish, bugs, and sea creatures."
    />
  </head>

  <body class="project-page">
    <%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.preBodyContent %>

    <a class="home-link" href="/">Home</a>

    <div class="header">
      <div class="emoji">
        <%= require('../../assets/projects/emoji/check-mark-button.svg') %>
      </div>
      <h1><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %></h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <ul class="badge-list">
        <li>2020</li>
        <li>Preact</li>
        <li>Netlify Identity</li>
        <li>FaunaDB -> MongoDB</li>
        <li>Jest</li>
        <li>Enzyme</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        A tracking system for your Animal Crossing New Horizons fish, bugs, and
        sea creatures. Once you log in and mark everything that you have caught
        so far, you will get a monthly email notifying you of what you have left
        to catch for that specific month.
      </p>

      <p>
        <a href="https://ac-tracker.netlify.app/" target="_blank"
          >Check it out!</a
        >
      </p>

      <p>
        <a
          href="https://youtube.com/shorts/UV1GZ2muxO0?feature=share"
          target="_blank"
          >Mobile Demo</a
        >
        |
        <a href="https://youtu.be/tFFHYAngr5k" target="_blank">Desktop Demo</a>
      </p>

      <p>
        I originally made it for myself, but anyone can use it - just create an
        account and track your catches!
      </p>

      <p>Sample email:</p>

      <img
        class="project-image ac-tracker-email-image"
        src="<%= require('../../assets/projects/ac-tracker-email.jpg') %>"
        alt="AC Tracker Email Screenshot"
        loading="lazy"
      />

      <p>
        Source code in the
        <a href="https://github.com/JesseKuntz/acnh-tracker" target="_blank"
          >Github repository</a
        >.
      </p>
    </div>

    <%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.postBodyContent %>
  </body>
</html>
